  "Description": {
    "English": "A highly energized form of <span class=\"name name-technology\">Cobalt</span>, this processed metal can be used to create <span class=\"name name-commodity\">Advanced Ion Batteries</span>, a conveniently portable source of energy for the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Exosuit</span>.<br><br>In widespread use as a key component in the creation of <span class=\"name name-technology\">advanced technologies and structures</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "<span class=\"name name-technology\">钴</span>的高能形态，这种加工后的金属可用于制造<span class=\"name name-commodity\">高级离子电池</span>，是一种轻便的便携式<span class=\"name name-technology\">套装</span>能量源。<br><br>广泛用于创建<span class=\"name name-technology\">高级技术和建筑</span> 的关键组件。",
    "TencentChinese": "<span class=\"name name-technology\">钴</span>的高能形态，这种加工后的金属可用于制造<span class=\"name name-commodity\">高级离子电池</span>，是一种轻便的便携式<span class=\"name name-technology\">套装</span>能量源。<br><br>广泛用于创建<span class=\"name name-technology\">高级技术和建筑</span> 的关键组件。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-technology\">鈷</span>的高能量形態。這種加工金屬能用來製造<span class=\"name name-commodity\">先進離子電池</span>，方便隨時隨地補充<span class=\"name name-technology\">強化套裝</span>能量。<br><br>用途廣泛，是製作<span class=\"name name-technology\">先進科技與結構</span>的重要元件。"
  },
