  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "<span class=\"name name-technology\">Ionized Cobalt</span> is created from Cobalt in a <span class=\"name name-technology\">Refiner</span>. Locate Cobalt underground.<br>Locate natural cave entrances. <span class=\"name name-red\">WARNING:</span> many caves contain hazardous flora.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "<span class=\"name name-technology\">离子钴</span>可用<span class=\"name name-technology\">精炼机</span>从钴中制得。定位地下的钴。<br>寻找天然洞穴的入口。<span class=\"name name-red\">警告：</span>许多洞穴中存在危险植物群系。",
    "TencentChinese": "<span class=\"name name-technology\">离子钴</span>可用<span class=\"name name-technology\">精炼机</span>从钴中制得。定位地下的钴。<br>寻找天然洞穴的入口。<span class=\"name name-red\">警告：</span>许多洞穴中存在危险植物群系。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-technology\">離子化鈷</span>是透過使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">精製機</span>從鈷製造出來的。找出地底下的鈷。<br>找出天然洞穴入口。<span class=\"name name-red\">警告：</span>許多洞穴內有危險植物。"
  },
